00:02:59,346 --> 00:03:02,474
This guy. He's here already.

13
00:03:04,393 --> 00:03:05,561
Lenny!

14
00:03:06,228 --> 00:03:08,021
It's Leonard.

15
00:03:09,690 --> 00:03:12,860
- Like I told you before.
- Did you? I must have forgot.

16
00:03:14,570 --> 00:03:16,697
I guess I've already told you
about my condition.

17
00:03:16,822 --> 00:03:19,491
Oh, well, only every time I see you.

18
00:03:28,250 --> 00:03:31,044
- My car.
- This is your car.

19
00:03:31,170 --> 00:03:32,629
Oh, you're in a playful mood.

20
00:03:34,256 --> 00:03:38,093
- It's not good to make fun of a handicap.
- Just trying to have a little fun.

21
00:03:42,264 --> 00:03:44,266
<font color="#40a040">[starts engine]</font>

22
00:03:45,142 --> 00:03:48,187
- Roll up your window.
- Hm?

23
00:03:53,192 --> 00:03:55,402
- It's broken.
- I can get that fixed for you.

24
00:03:56,695 --> 00:03:59,740
- So, where to, Sherlock?
- I got a lead on a place.

25
00:03:59,865 --> 00:04:03,118
- What the hell you wanna go there for?
- You know it?

26
00:04:03,243 --> 00:04:05,913
Yeah, it's just this fucked up building.
